Release info:

This CD was Part of the PUBLIC WORKS box-set in co-operation with Shepard Fairey. The box was limited to 450 units, contains 5 different Obey T-Shirts, a Shepard Fairey hardcover book (69 pages), a bag of stickers and some batches.

Self-released megamix CD by DJ Shadow in cooperation with underground artist Obey. At approximately 45 minutes into the mix, both Lateef The Truth Speaker and Lyrics Born make a brief MC appearance.

This mix includes tracks by Beastie Boys, Public Enemy, David Banner, and Young MC as well as "Baby Mama" by Three 6 Mafia, "What Happened To That Boy?" by Baby, "Burn Rubber" by Too Short, "Them Girls" by Silkk The Shocker, and "3 Freaks" by DJ Shadow feat. Keak Da Sneak & Turf Talk.
